  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons of oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and bell pepper and cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced bacon and cook until crispy, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the smoked chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5-6 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced almonds, cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and pepper. Stir to combine.",
